 ore chaos? This Bloody Wedding is an immersive comedy by TIA Theatre Compan
 y. Inspired by Telenovela style\, This Bloody Wedding brings to life the dr
 eam of crashing a wedding and living the drama as your own. No two performa
 nces are the same. Each night offers a different perspective by a different
  character and timeline. Revealing new layers of the story with every visit
 . Expect love\, notice the lies\, and make sure you count the heads! After 
 all\, this is not just a wedding... It´s a Telenovela. Do you think you’
